<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Harvest Bistro Menu</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="menu-container">
        <h1>Today's Selections</h1>

        <section class="section" id="appetizers">
            <h2>Appetizers</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <h3>Sun-Dried Tomato Crostini</h3>
                    <p>Crunchy baguette slices topped with whipped feta and sun-dried tomato spread.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Honey Glazed Cauliflower Bites</h3>
                    <p>Crispy cauliflower florets drizzled with honey sriracha glaze and sesame seeds.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Avocado Shrimp Cups</h3>
                    <p>Chilled shrimp served in avocado halves with lime crema and cilantro.</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="section" id="main-course">
            <h2>Main Course</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <h3>Herb Crusted Lamb Chops</h3>
                    <p>Juicy lamb chops with rosemary and thyme crust, served with garlic mashed potatoes.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Seared Tuna Steak</h3>
                    <p>Pan-seared tuna served with sesame rice and ginger soy reduction.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Mushroom Risotto</h3>
                    <p>Creamy arborio rice slow-cooked with wild mushrooms and truffle oil.</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="section" id="desserts">
            <h2>Desserts</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <h3>Lemon Berry Tart</h3>
                    <p>Buttery tart shell filled with lemon custard and topped with fresh berries.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Salted Caramel Pudding</h3>
                    <p>Rich caramel pudding with sea salt flakes and whipped cream topping.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Matcha Ice Cream Sandwich</h3>
                    <p>Green tea ice cream between soft vanilla cookies, served chilled.</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>